data.description: Lovely craftsman style home situated on almost 1/4 acre corner lot in West Georgetown. This property has a very open & flowing floor plan- With three bedrooms, two full bathrooms, an extra living space that could function as an extra dining area, a formal entry area, a large front porch & a large screened in patio space.      The home has many upgrades & recent updates- Including granite countertops in the kitchen & master bathroom, upgraded designer laminate flooring, a new privacy fence, a new shed & newer stainless steel appliances.    A quick commute to downtown Austin, Round Rock & Temple. Close to shopping, schools, many public parks, swimming holes, major highways & so many wonderful destinations that Geotgetown residents enjoy.
